<definition-item><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">F28G1/00</classification-symbol><definition-title>Non-rotary, e.g. reciprocated, appliances  (<class-ref scheme="cpc">F28G3/00</class-ref> takes precedence)</definition-title><definition-statement>
